title: Bug 4121: JarExporter causes out of Sync
description: Bug 4121: JarExporter causes out of Sync
OB: If you export a directory (project) and place the exported jar in the same directory (project), then you will get an out of sync message when you try to overwrite the exported jar file for the second time.
SR:
To reproduce the issue, follow these steps:
1. Export a directory (project) to a jar file.
2. Place the exported jar file in the same directory (project).
3. Try to overwrite the exported jar file for the second time.
